<tbody><tr>
<td><ul id="plainSister" style="display:inline-block; font-size:93%; line-height:normal; list-style-type:none; list-style-image:none; list-style-position:outside; border:1px solid #AAA; float:right; clear:right; margin:0.5ex 0.5ex 0.5ex 0.5ex; padding:0.0ex 0.0ex 0.0ex 0.0ex; background:#FFFFFF; background-color:#FFFFFF;"><li class="sisitem"><span class="sisicon" style="padding-right:1ex;"><span typeof="mw:File/Frameless"><a href="/wiki/%E0%AC%AC%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%B6%E0%AD%87%E0%AC%B7:SiteMatrix" title="ବିଶେଷ:SiteMatrix"><img alt="Sister Projects." src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Wikimedia-logo.svg/18px-Wikimedia-logo.svg.png" decoding="async" width="18" height="18" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Wikimedia-logo.svg/27px-Wikimedia-logo.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Wikimedia-logo.svg/36px-Wikimedia-logo.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="1024" data-file-height="1024"/></a></span></span><a href="/wiki/%E0%AC%AC%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%B6%E0%AD%87%E0%AC%B7:SiteMatrix" title="ବିଶେଷ:SiteMatrix">sister projects</a>: <a href="https://or.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%AC%89%E0%AC%87%E0%AC%95%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%AA%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%A1%E0%AC%BC%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%86:%E0%AC%B2%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%96%E0%AC%A8_%E0%AC%B6%E0%AD%88%E0%AC%B3%E0%AD%80" class="extiw" title="w:ଉଇକିପିଡ଼ିଆ:ଲିଖନ ଶୈଳୀ">Wikipedia article</a>, <a href="https://or.wikiquote.org/wiki/Wikiquote:Manual_of_style" class="extiw" title="q:Wikiquote:Manual of style">quotes</a>, <a href="https://or.wikinews.org/wiki/Wikinews:Style_guide" class="extiw" title="n:Wikinews:Style guide">news</a>, <a href="https://or.wikibooks.org/wiki/Wikibooks:Manual_of_Style" class="extiw" title="b:Wikibooks:Manual of Style">textbook</a>, <a href="https://or.wikiversity.org/wiki/Wikiversity:Manual_of_Style" class="extiw" title="v:Wikiversity:Manual of Style">course</a>, <a href="https://or.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Wikivoyage:Manual_of_style" class="extiw" title="voy:Wikivoyage:Manual of style">travel guide</a>, <a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q4994848" class="extiw" title="d:Q4994848">Wikidata item</a>.</li></ul>This <b>Manual of Style</b> outlines Wikisource's formatting conventions and guidelines (see <a href="https://or.wikipedia.org/wiki/style_guide" class="extiw" title="w:style guide">Wikipedia's article on style guides</a>). These are not hard <i>rules</i>, and can be ignored where necessary. However, users should follow these guidelines where possible to ensure that Wikisource is consistent and maintains a high standard of quality.<br clear="all"/>
<div style="float:right;padding:5px; margin:0 0 1em 1em; border-left:1px solid #000;">
<p><b><a class="mw-selflink selflink">Style guide</a></b>
</p>
<ul><li><a href="/w/index.php?title=%E0%AC%89%E0%AC%87%E0%AC%95%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%AA%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%A0%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%97%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%B0:Image_guidelines&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="ଉଇକିପାଠାଗାର:Image guidelines (ପୃଷ୍ଠାଟି ନାହିଁ)">Images</a></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=%E0%AC%89%E0%AC%87%E0%AC%95%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%AA%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%A0%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%97%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%B0:Style_guide/Tables&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="ଉଇକିପାଠାଗାର:Style guide/Tables (ପୃଷ୍ଠାଟି ନାହିଁ)">Tables</a></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=%E0%AC%89%E0%AC%87%E0%AC%95%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%AA%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%A0%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%97%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%B0:Style_guide/Orthography&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="ଉଇକିପାଠାଗାର:Style guide/Orthography (ପୃଷ୍ଠାଟି ନାହିଁ)">Orthography</a></li></ul>
